	* libproto/imap/mbox.c (_imap_env_date): Return a 0-terminated
	string.

	Fix MH test suite.

	The ali-everybody tests fails on machines with user database kept
	in a non-standard storage (e.g. LDAP or NIS).  This patch
	attempts to
	fix it.

