	* mh/tests/.gitignore: Add lu.
	* mh/tests/Makefile.am (noinst_PROGRAMS): New variable.
	* mh/tests/ali.at: Use lu instead of scanning /etc/passwd
	directly.

2012-05-13  Sergey Poznyakoff  <gray@gnu.org.ua>

