2012-01-08  Sergey Poznyakoff  <gray@gnu.org.ua>

	Restore extra quoting in test mhn-store-pipe of mh/tests/mhn.at

	Extra quoting is necessary because the argument includes
	unbalanced
	parentheses.  It was first implemented in commit 1b5098c9 on
	2011-05-05,
	but was accidentally removed in commit 1e33c774 on 2011-10-16.

