	mode, parse
	everything at once.
	Handle continuation responses in client mode.
	(mu_imapio_getline): Toggle MU_XSCRIPT_PAYLOAD only if requested.
	* libmailutils/imapio/literal.c: Wait for continuation response
	(in
	client mode).
