	* libmu_dbm/dbm.c (_mu_dbm_init): Rename mu_dbm_init. All uses
	changed.
	Use URL composing interface to create hints.
	* maidag/maidag.c (mu_dbm_get_hint): New function.
	* pop3d/pop3d.c (cb2_forward_file_checks): Use
