	* pop3d/apop.c (pop3d_apopuser): Use configured database name and
	safety flags, if set.
	* pop3d/pop3d.h [ENABLE_DBM] (APOP_PASSFILE): Add ".db" suffix.
	(apop_database_name, apop_database_safety)
	(apop_database_safety_set): New variables.

