	Fix locking in pop3 and imap4d.  This complements d0769b4f.

	* lib/manlock.c (mailbox_open_and_lock): Open mailbox before
	retrieving
	its locker, otherwise it is always NULL.
	* pop3d/pop3d.c (main): Enforce mandatory locking.

