	mh: open mailboxes in read-only mode unless the requested
	operation mandates otherwise.

	* mh/mhn.c: Open mailbox in read-only mode.
	* mh/mhseq.c: Likewise.
	* mh/scan.c: Likewise.
	* mh/pick.c: If sequences are given, open mailbox for RW,
	otherwise
	open it for reading only.

