	(_cb_include): Remove unnecessary code.
	(mu_build_container): Simplify. All uses updated.
	(mu_cfg_tree_reduce): Simplify invocation. All uses updated.

	* libmu_argp/muinit.c (mu_app_init): Re-implement --config-help
	support.

