	Rewrite temporary file handling.

	* include/mailutils/util.h (mu_make_file_name_suf): New proto.
	(mu_make_file_name): Replace with a macro.
	(MU_TEMPFILE_TMPDIR,MU_TEMPFILE_SUFFIX)
	(MU_TEMPFILE_MKDIR): New flags.
