	* libmailutils/tests/Makefile.am (noinst_PROGRAMS): Add tempfile.

2010-11-25  Sergey Poznyakoff  <gray@gnu.org.ua>

	mhn: minor changes.

	* mh/etc/mhl.headers: New file.
	* mh/etc/Makefile.am (MH_FILES): Add mhl.headers.
