	* NEWS: Update for version 2.1
	* configure.ac: Update for version 2.1
	(AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE): Add dist-lzma and dist-xz.
	* bootstrap (slurp): Remove call to silentize:
	not needed with recent gnulib.

