	Remove. (mu_wicket_set_ticket): Remove. (mu_wicket_get_ticket):
	Change proto. (mu_wicket_set_destroy, mu_wicket_set_data)
	(mu_wicket_get_data, mu_wicket_set_get_ticket): New
