2008-02-05  Sergey Poznyakoff  <gray@gnu.org.ua>

	* pop3d/extra.c (pop3d_readline): After a failed authorization
	attempt many clients simply disconnect without issuing QUIT. 
	Do not count this as a protocol error.    

