	(mu_folder_create_from_record): Set mu_folder_match as the default
	matcher.
	(mu_folder_set_match, mu_folder_get_match): New functions.
	(mu_folder_enumerate): New function.
	(mu_folder_list): Rewrite using mu_folder_enumerate.

