	and logging levels.

2007-11-29  Sergey Poznyakoff  <gray@gnu.org.ua>

	* comsat/action.c, comsat/comsat.c, imap4d/auth_gsasl.c,
	imap4d/auth_gss.c, imap4d/authenticate.c, imap4d/bye.c,
