	(mu_refcount_value): New function.
	(mu_refcount_create,mu_refcount_destroy,mu_refcount_inc)
	(mu_refcount_dec): Fix monitor usage.
	(mu_refcount_inc,mu_refcount_dec): Fix return type.
	
