	* THANKS: Add Willem Jaap Zwart
	* NEWS: Update
	* imap4d/imap4d.h (is_atom): New function
	* imap4d/list.c (print_file,print_dir): Rewrite using an
	auxiliary function. Make sure the string is properly quoted if it
	is not a valid atom.
