2005-03-08  Sergey Poznyakoff 

	TODO:121 said: "file viewer, based on the mimetypes api. I want to do
	a "v foo.blah", have it look up .blah in mime.types, and do the 
	action spec'ed in mailcap."
	So, here it goes:

	* mimeview: New directory
