2005-02-21  Sergey Poznyakoff

	* libsieve/actions.c: Further unification of diagnostic style.
	* libsieve/argp.c: Likewise.
	* mail/mail.c: Likewise.
	* mail.local/mailquota.c: Likewise.
	* mailbox/mu_argp.c: Likewise.
