	* imap4d/unsubscribe.c: Rewritten. Thanks Andrew Barnes
	for reporting the bug.

2005-02-03  Sergey Poznyakoff

	* guimb/main.c (parse_opt): Use arg instead of optarg.
	Thanks James Dolter for reporting.

