	auth_state instead of state. Possibly this was a typo...
	* mailbox/include/imap0.h (struct _f_imap.capac): Changed
	type to int.
	* mailbox/maildir/mbox.c (maildir_gethostname): Fixed a gross
	memory allocation bug.

