        * mailbox/mu_auth.c (mu_auth_data_alloc): Fixed COPY macro.
	* mh/mhn.c (main): Ignore sighups.
	* mh/mh_format.c (builtin_formataddr): Bugfix.

2003-03-26  Sergey Poznyakoff

