2003-02-03  Sergey Poznyakoff

	* auth/Makefile.am: Removed leftover AUTH_AUTHOBJS from LIBADD
	* auth/gsasl.c (buffer_grow, _gsasl_strerror): Fixed declarations.
	* auth/tls.c (_tls_strerror): Fixed declaration.
