	* guimb/scm/sieve-core.scm: Added :regex tag -- an
	  extension allowing to use posix regexp in address
	  and header tests.
	* mh/repl.c: New file. A framework for the `repl' program.
	* mh/Makefile.am: Added repl
	* mh/.cvsignore: Likewise.

