	* acconfig.h: Added WITH_GUILE define.
	* configure.in: Define WITH_GUILE. Added mail.local.
	* Makefile.am: Added mail.local.

	* guimb/run_scm.c: Deleted.
	* guimb/Makefile.am: Removed run_scm.c
